\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 ME\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Lisa and I argue every now and then and one of the things I\'92ve learned is that while I can compartmentalize, she doesn\'92t do that well.  And while there are something that are unsettled in our relationship we\'92re on hold.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 Transition:  No one in life likes to be stuck and yet that is what happens.   \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Last week we talked about being stuck and we even gave out cards\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This week I want to talk to you about the solution to being stuck in our walk with God because what happens is we get have some stuff to settle but we get stuck sitting down and today I\'92m going to challenge you to settle it today.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 Transition:  God says something to His people in a passage I want to read to you this morning about settling\'85\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 GOD\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf3 \'93Come now, let us settle the matter,\'94\uc0\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 says the\'a0Lord.\uc0\u8232 \'93Though your sins are like scarlet,\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 they shall be as white as snow;\uc0\u8232 though they are red as crimson,\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 they shall be like wool.\uc0\u8232 
\fs18 \super 19\'a0
\fs24 \nosupersub If you are willing and obedient,\uc0\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 you will eat the good things of the land;\uc0\u8232 
\fs18 \super 20\'a0
\fs24 \nosupersub but if you resist and rebel,\uc0\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 you will be devoured by the sword.\'94\uc0\u8232 For the mouth of the\'a0Lord\'a0has spoken.   Isaiah 1\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 YOU\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 Seeker\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The person who sits here is waiting for proof.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They don\'92t have all the answers and they don\'92t feel as though they can make a decision until they do.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The problem is I can\'92t nor can anyone else prove God to you\'85if they say that they are very na\'efve or trying to sell you something.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But you can\'92t prove God doesn\'92t exist.  All you can do with matters like this is look at the world we live and what we do know and come to the most logical conclusion.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 Illustration of me reading an article about the fine tune nature of dark energy and other issues in space that if off even a little would end life instantly\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We see it over and over again there has to be someone or something that has organized the worlds.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Even our own DNA is mapped out in an intelligent way the points toward someone writing it out like a code\'85it isn\'92t random.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I could go on and on but that isn\'92t the point\'85the point is that you have faith in something\'85you just have to settle the matter!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf3 Now faith is confidence in what we hope for\'a0and assurance about what we do not see.\'a0  Hebrews 11:1\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now some people will say they don\'92t believe in anything they can\'92t see or prove\'85that isn\'92t true.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t see or test love.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How to settle it and stand up:  Put your faith in Jesus, not in what you can prove \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 Skeptic\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This person maybe has been to church but left.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They\'92ve been hurt by some people in the church and don\'92t want to go back.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I know Christians vs I know Jesus.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The problem is when you communicate this what you are communicating is that you put your faith in people and not God\'85let me promise you\'85people will always let you down.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 23\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Let us hold unswervingly to the hope\'a0we profess,\'a0for he who promised is faithful.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Who is faithful?  Jesus\'85not Christians\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92ve said it before and I mean it, I will let you down eventually as a pastor.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I ADORE my wife and I fail her, if I\'92m going to fail her I promise I\'92m going to fail you!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 24\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub And let us consider how we may spur one another on toward love and good deeds,
\f3\b\fs18 \super 25\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub not giving up meeting together,\'a0as some are in the habit of doing\'85  Heb 10\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How to settle it and stand up:  Put your confidence in Jesus, not in people\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\
\
\
\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 Spiritual\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Two types:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m spiritual but not moral\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When people tell me they are spiritual here is what I hear:  I want to be able to do what I want, when I want, with whoever I want, and have no accountability, no community that shares my beliefs, and I don\'92t want anyone to tell me I\'92m wrong or what to do.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is saying you want to have one foot in one world and one foot in another\'85settle it\'85pick one\'85but don\'92t think you are fooling God.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m spiritual and a good person.\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The church is full of these people\'85even today\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You may fool people around you but you aren\'92t fooling Him\'85He knows your heart!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf3 Stop bringing meaningless offerings!\uc0\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 Your incense\'a0is detestable\'a0to me.\
\uc0\u8232 New Moons,\'a0Sabbaths and convocations\'97\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 I cannot bear your worthless assemblies.\
\uc0\u8232 
\f1\fs18 \super 14\'a0
\f2\fs24 \nosupersub Your New Moon\'a0feasts and your appointed festivals\uc0\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 I hate with all my being.\
\uc0\u8232 They have become a burden to me;\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 I am weary\'a0of bearing them.\
\uc0\u8232 
\f1\fs18 \super 15\'a0
\f2\fs24 \nosupersub When you spread out your hands\'a0in prayer,\uc0\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 I hide\'a0my eyes from you;\
\uc0\u8232 even when you offer many prayers,\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 I am not listening.  Isaiah 1\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can do the right thing with the wrong heart and it doesn\'92t help\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can do the wrong things with the right heart and it doesn\'92t help\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Only when you put your trust in Jesus does it matter\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Question \'96 When you think about whether you are good with God or not\'85do you point to a moment where you committed your life to Jesus or do think about how you are a good person?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How to settle it and stand up:  Put your trust in Jesus, not in your works\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 Sinner\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some Christians seem to just have a bad attitude\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I call them Eyore Christians\'85something always bad is happening in their world\'85they\'92re always losing their tale and they seem to be ok with it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Their world is messed up, their relationships are broken, their in poor health, their finances are messed up, but don\'92t worry\'85because one day their going to die, and then they\'92ll get to go to heaven and it will be ok!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are not just a sinner saved by grace!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf3 Since, then, you have been raised with Christ,\'a0set your hearts on things above, where Christ is, seated at the right hand of God.\'a0
\f1\fs18 \super 2\'a0
\f2\fs24 \nosupersub Set your minds on things above, not on earthly things.\'a0  Col 3\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How to settle it and stand up:  Have a resurrection mindset, not just faith in a resurrection miracle\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I don\'92t what\'92s dead in your life but I know a God who is in the business of resurrecting things\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I don\'92t know what pain you have but I know a healer who heals people\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are a child of God, the redeemed, exalted, lifted up, cared for, loved, and protected.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This week I want you all to do two things:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Get up first thing in the morning and ask God, what is the one thing you want me to do\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Pick one area of your life and start to pray that God would resurrect it!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
